code: public static ParamsBuilder paramsBuilder() {     return new ParamsBuilder(). }
public ParamsBuilder variable(Object value) {     params.add(new Var(value)).     return this. }
public ParamsBuilder agg(AggregateFunctionAttribute agg) {     params.add(new Agg(agg)).     return this. }
public ParamsBuilder grouping(GroupingFunctionAttribute grouping) {     params.add(new Grouping(grouping)).     return this. }
public ParamsBuilder script(Params ps) {     params.add(new Script(ps)).     return this. }
public Params build() {     return new Params(new ArrayList<>(params)). }
